data.description: Spend Christmas in this charming home located just steps from the Whistle Stop in historic downtown Glendale. The house has real bamboo flooring. it has large utility building on the lot. Sit on the front porch and see the beautiful view. Or walk out onto the back porch that goes out onto a new concrete patio. Has large rooms and eat in kitchen. Central heat and air. Call for a showing 270-735-6748
